Package biz.gabrys.lesscss.compiler2

The LessCSS Compiler compiles Less source files to the CSS code.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Less175CompilerOptionsBuilder.OperatingSystemChecker
    Responsible for checking operating system family.
    LessCompiler
    Responsible for executing Less compiler for sources files.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Less175Compiler
    Default implementation of the LessCompiler.
    Less175CompilerOptionsBuilder
    Options that control the Less compilation process.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Less175CompilerOptionsBuilder.LineNumbersValue
    Available values for line numbers option.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CompilerException
    Thrown to indicate that an error occurred during compilation process.
    InitializationException
    Thrown to indicate that an error occurred during compiler initialization.
    ResolveImportException
    Thrown to indicate that an error occurred while resolving imports.
    SyntaxException
    Thrown to indicate that a syntax error occurred during source file compilation.
